tep 1: Download the java, hadoop and spark and place in under home path

Step 2: Add the below paramter to bashrc file under home path.

export  JAVA_HOME=/home/hari/workspace/jdk1.8.0_361

export  SPARK_HOME=/home/hari/workspace/spark-3.2.3-bin-hadoop2.7

export  HADOOP_HOME=/home/hari/workspace/hadoop-2.10.2

export  PATH=JAVA_HOME/bin:$HADOOP_HOME/bin:$SPARK_HOME/bin:$PATH

step 3: source the bashrc file

hari@hps17:~$ source .bashrc
Welcome!!

Step 4: Daemon process 


